    "title": "guix: Brainstorm w/re guix.sigs repo layout",
    "body": "A few ideas for modernizing the layout as we're creating a new `guix.sigs` repo:\r\n\r\n1. Hierarchy would look something like: `guix.sigs/$TAG/$HOST(-codesigned)/$SIGNER/SHA256SUMS`\r\n2. We can move `contrib/gitian-keys` to this new `guix.sigs` repo\r\n\r\nThese are just some initial thoughts, please let me know if this sounds reasonable without bike-shedding ðŸ˜¬  \r\n",
